timestamp.Description: a continuously increasing identifier of the sampling time registered by the device

x_coordinate.Description: Gaze position x-coordinate of the recorded eye, in the coordinate units specified in the corresponding metadata sidecar.

y_coordinate.Description: Gaze position y-coordinate of the recorded eye, in the coordinate units specified in the corresponding metadata sidecar.

pupil_size.Description: Pupil area of the recorded eye as calculated by the eye-tracker in arbitrary units (see EyeLink's documentation for conversion).
